      • capture

        public CaptureResponseDto capture(String url,
                                  Object request,
                                  Class<?> responseType)
                           throws RegBaseCheckedException
        Description copied from interface: IMosipBioDeviceIntegrator
        Captures the biometric details from the Bio device through MDM service

        This will accept the url where the biometric device will be running and a request data object which will specify exactly what biometric we are requesting for e.g finger, iris, face and will the return a response containing the bytes of the scanned data along with some other detail such as quality score of the scanned data

        Specified by:
        capture in interface IMosipBioDeviceIntegrator
        Parameters:
        url - - device info MDM service url
        request - - request for capture biometric
        responseType - - response format
        Returns:
        CaptureResponseDto - the captured biometric details
        Throws:
        RegBaseCheckedException - - generalized exception with errorCode and errorMessage
